{"tid":1918730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★疫情影響手機銷售 大陸 iPhone 銷量急挫六成","createTime":"2020-03-10T09:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T12:07:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"08c4ac225590f5356a85f82491767ab45ddd1500","tid":1918730,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎由 1 月起於中國大陸爆發，很多城市都鼓勵市民減少外出，很多商場和店舖都因此需要關門。受到疫情的影響，iPhone 於大陸的銷量亦在 2 月份大跌。根據大陸官方的數字，2 月份 iPhone 只售出 49.4 萬部，相比去年同期的 127 萬部，按年下跌了六成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/10/apple-sold-just-500000-iphones-in-china-in-february-as-coronavirus-hit/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F10%2Fapple-sold-just-500000-iphones-in-china-in-february-as-coronavirus-hit%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=e161437e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/10/apple-sold-just-500000-iphones-in-china-in-february-as-coronavirus-hit/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"033deddebed0150a0ea76af00ddeb3abed67b4c2","tid":1918730,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f607ac4b7af29ff322ab2f544d91fc5e2ea2c8c","tid":1918730,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"Chi na no idog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01eb59a536a5e5dd56762eba0aed838b7102e8a2","tid":1918730,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"實情係啲支那人買哂華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hk